snippet.title: Robot Detour - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description: Join a robot on an adventure to help his friends in Robot Detour! Check out the Robot Detour trailer for this upcoming puzzle game about a wired robot who delivers batteries to his wireless friends. Robot Detour will be available on Steam on November 14, 2024.
